      description: "Sports organisations investing heavily in elite performance see minimal return on that investment in fan engagement, merchandise revenue and broadcast value. Without a digital touchpoint — a club app, live scoring, social content integration — fans consume their sport through third-party platforms rather than the club's own channels.",
