      description: "Council leisure centres, club facilities and commercial gyms relying on phone bookings or basic online forms create unnecessary friction for members. Double-bookings, peak-time overloads and no-shows cost revenue and damage member satisfaction. Modern members expect instant, real-time booking from their phone.",
